'''原碳酸'''是一种假想的[[酸|酸]]或[[官能团|官能团]]，化学式H<sub>4</sub>CO<sub>4</sub>。它是带有RC(OH)<sub>3</sub>结构的一种酸。<ref>[http://www.chem.qmul.ac.uk/iupac/class/carba.html#25 Carboxylic Acids and Derivatives] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chem.qmul.ac.uk/iupac/class/carba.html#25 |date=20170913060101 }} IUPAC Recommendations on Organic & Biochemical Nomenclature</ref> 

在一个原碳酸分子中，碳原子与4个[[羟基|羟基]]以共价键相连。这种化合物至今未被发现，因为它极不稳定，立刻分解为[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]和[[水|水]]。<ref name=Bohm1997>{{cite journal | author = Bohm, S. | coauthors = Antipova, D.; Kuthan, J. | year = 1997 | title = A Study of Methanetetraol Dehydration to Carbonic Acid | journal = International Journal of Quantum Chemistry | volume = 62 | pages = 315–322
 | doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1097-461X(1997)62:3<315::AID-QUA10>3.3.CO;2-N}}</ref> 原碳酸是一种[[四元酸|四元酸]]，理论上可以形成4种盐，比如NaH<sub>3</sub>CO<sub>4</sub>（原碳酸三氢钠）、 Na<sub>2</sub>H<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>4</sub>（原碳酸二氢钠）、Na<sub>3</sub>HCO<sub>4</sub>（原碳酸一氢钠）、和 Na<sub>4</sub>CO<sub>4</sub>（原碳酸钠）。

原碳酸可以作为[[官能团|官能团]]。例如，它可以形成[[原碳酸四乙酯|原碳酸四乙酯]]，可以用[[三氯硝基甲烷|三氯硝基甲烷]]和[[乙醇钠|乙醇钠]]在乙醇中製取。<ref>[http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/orgsyn/prepContent.asp?prep=cv4p0457 Orthocarbonic acid, tetraethyl ester] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/orgsyn/prepContent.asp?prep=cv4p0457 |date=20120920183920 }} ''Organic Syntheses'', Coll. Vol. 4, p.457 (1963); Vol. 32, p.68 (1952)</ref> 另外，聚原碳酸稳定，可以用于吸收污水中的有机溶剂，<ref name=Sonmez2005>{{cite journal | author = Sonmez, H.B. | coauthors = Wudl, F. | year = 2005 | title = Cross-linked poly (orthocarbonate) s as organic solvent sorbents |journal=Macromolecules |volume=38 |issue=5 |pages=1623–1626 |doi=10.1021/ma048731x')}}</ref>或用于牙科还原材料。<ref name=Stansbury1992>{{cite journal | author = Stansbury, J.W. | year = 1992 | title = Synthesis and evaluation of new oxaspiro monomers for double ring-opening polymerization | journal = Journal of Dental Research | volume = 71 | issue = 7 | pages = 1408–1412 | url = http://jdr.iadrjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/71/7/1408 | accessdate = 2008-06-19 | doi = 10.1177/00220345920710070901 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080708223634/http://jdr.iadrjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/71/7/1408 | archivedate = 2008-07-08 }}</ref>

